OL,3,CShannon Matthews' kidnapper dies from
OL,4,Ccancer
OL,6,FThe man who was convicted of
OL,7,Fkidnapping schoolgirl Shannon Matthews
OL,8,Fhas died from cancer.
OL,10,FMichael Donovan, who was 54, died at
OL,11,Fthe Three Valleys Hospital in
OL,12,Fyesterday, 16 April.
OL,14,FDonovan hatched in , West Yorkshire,
OL,15,Fin 2008 in a bid to claim #50,000
OL,16,Fworth of reward money for the nine-
OL,17,Fyear-old's safe return.
OL,19,FHe held Shannon captive in his flat in
OL,20,Fa draw beneath a bed for 28 days.
