OL,6,FDonovan had stayed at Three Valleys
OL,7,FHospital, which specialises in caring
OL,8,Ffor people with complex mental health
OL,9,Fissues, for the last six years.
OL,11,FIt is reported he had been diagnosed
OL,12,Fwith stage three throat cancer in
OL,13,FFebruary and given months to live.
OL,15,FIn a statement, West Yorkshire Police
OL,16,Fsaid: "Police were contacted on
OL,17,FTuesday, 16 April and made aware of
OL,18,Fthe death of a man in hospital in the
OL,19,FSteeton area.
