OL,6,FIn what became its biggest inquiry
OL,7,Fsince the search for Yorkshire Ripper
OL,8,FPeter Sutcliffe, West Yorkshire Police
OL,9,Fspent over #3m looking for her.
OL,11,FShannon was found tied up and drugged
OL,12,Fin a draw underneath Donovan's bed on
OL,13,F14 March 2008. Donovan, Karen Matthews
OL,14,Fand her then boyfriend Craig Meehan
OL,15,Fwere arrested in connection with the
OL,16,Fdisappearance.
