OL,6,FDonovan and Matthews were jailed for
OL,7,Feight years for the kidnapping. He was
OL,8,Freleased from prison in 2012 but had
OL,9,Fbeen cared for in hospital settings
OL,10,Ffollowing his release.
OL,12,FMatthews was given a new identity on
OL,13,Fher release from prison and her
OL,14,Fdaughter Shannon was granted lifelong
OL,15,Fanonymity.
OL,17,FIn 2017 Shannon's grandparents
OL,19,FActress Sheridan Smith starred as the
OL,20,Fmother who led the community search
OL,21,Ffor the nine-year-old in The Moorside.
